metadata.name: what is it?
metadata.description:
mindscapecanvas_unboxing_what-is-it.png, 2048 x 2048 px, 72 dpi, AI-generated art, created in 2023 by mindscapecanvas.

A piece from the first NFT collection 'unboxing'. Unique minting, royalty-free and smart contract NFT.

The work is the result of a creative process in which I use different AIs to generate images. The individual steps are curated by changing parameters. So long, until in the end an expressive result is created.
